User/Human -> Interface AI [Requests/Interrupts]
User/Human -> External LLM [Alerts via Tailscale/SSH]
Interface AI -> Governance Team [Delegates Specs]
Governance Team -> Conductor [Oversees Projects]
Conductor -> MoE Agents [Coordinates]
Conductor -> Black Box Factory [Drives Lifecycle]
Auditor -> All Components [Audits/Escalates]
Auditor -> IRT Orchestrator [Triggers on Violations]
IRT Orchestrator -> IRT Agents [Manages Team]
IRT Orchestrator -> All Components [Quarantines/Remediates]
Black Box Factory -> Sandbox (Docker) [Runs In]
External LLM -> IRT Agents [Powers Roles]
Local LLM -> All Components [Powers Agents (Local)]
